{"nodes":[{"pos":[12,49],"content":"Compiler Error C2148 | Microsoft Docs","needQuote":false,"needEscape":true,"nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error C2148 | Microsoft Docs","pos":[0,37]}]},{"content":"Compiler Error C2148","pos":[598,618]},{"content":"total size of array must not exceed 0x7fffffff bytes","pos":[619,671]},{"content":"An array exceeds the limit.","pos":[678,705]},{"content":"Reduce the size of the array.","pos":[706,735]},{"content":"Example","pos":[744,751]},{"content":"The following sample generates C2148:","pos":[755,792]}],"content":"---\ntitle: \"Compiler Error C2148 | Microsoft Docs\"\nms.custom: \"\"\nms.date: \"11/04/2016\"\nms.reviewer: \"\"\nms.suite: \"\"\nms.technology: \n  - \"devlang-cpp\"\nms.tgt_pltfrm: \"\"\nms.topic: \"error-reference\"\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"C2148\"\ndev_langs: \n  - \"C++\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"C2148\"\nms.assetid: e510c2c9-7b57-4ce8-be03-ba363e2cc5d9\ncaps.latest.revision: 12\nauthor: \"corob-msft\"\nms.author: \"corob\"\nmanager: \"ghogen\"\ntranslation.priority.ht: \n  - \"cs-cz\"\n  - \"de-de\"\n  - \"es-es\"\n  - \"fr-fr\"\n  - \"it-it\"\n  - \"ja-jp\"\n  - \"ko-kr\"\n  - \"pl-pl\"\n  - \"pt-br\"\n  - \"ru-ru\"\n  - \"tr-tr\"\n  - \"zh-cn\"\n  - \"zh-tw\"\n---\n# Compiler Error C2148\ntotal size of array must not exceed 0x7fffffff bytes  \n  \n An array exceeds the limit. Reduce the size of the array.  \n  \n## Example  \n The following sample generates C2148:  \n  \n```  \n// C2148.cpp  \n#include <stdio.h>  \n#include <stdlib.h>  \n  \nint main( ) {  \n   char MyArray[0x7ffffffff];   // C2148  \n   char * MyArray2 = (char *)malloc(0x7fffffff);  \n  \n   if (MyArray2)  \n      printf_s(\"It worked!\");  \n   else  \n      printf_s(\"It didn't work.\");  \n}  \n```"}